msgid "Find out how to create and upload apps to the Firefox Marketplace:"
msgstr "Dysgwch sut i greu a llwytho i fyny apiau i'r Firefox Marketplace:"

#: marketplace/marketplace.lang:84
msgid "Develop HTML5 Web apps for the Firefox Marketplace »"
msgstr "Datblygwch apiau HTML5 Web ar gyfer y Firefox Marketplace »"

#: marketplace/marketplace.lang:88
msgid "Partner with Mozilla »"
msgstr "Dewch yn Bartner i Mozilla »"

#: marketplace/marketplace.lang:92
